node.text: What would you do if every 30 minutes equaled 1 year of your life? In writer/director M. Night Shyamalan’s new film ‘OLD’, that’s exactly what happens in this thriller/horror only in theaters this Friday. In celebration of the theme of ‘OLD’ I’ve done my take on an ‘OLD’ transformation because Time comes for us all #OldTheMovie @mnight @oldthemovie #ad
